Ralph Castain a &eacute;crit&nbsp;:
<blockquote cite="mid:AFB7469A-DD9A-4638-86CA-9BFA39275D09@lanl.gov"
 type="cite">I'm afraid that the changes in how we handle hostfiles
forced us to remove the default hostfile name. Beginning with 1.3, you
will need to specify it.
  <div><br>
  </div>
  <div>Note that you can do this in your etc/openmpi-mca-params.conf
file, if you want.</div>
  <div><br>
  </div>
  <div>Ralph</div>
